  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out our next cozy game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/5af33c38713d9a56e1d93d0aa43ab355.avif?t=1727815132\" width=644 height=177 /></span>Watermelon Suika Game also known as the Watermelon Game, is a casual and addictive game where the goal is to stack and combine fruits of different sizes to create larger watermelons. The game mechanics resemble a \"match-3\" style, but with a fun twist where the fruits fall and roll across the screen with dynamic physics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/945604759fa9e6435c4e84a130df3853.poster.avif?t=1727815132\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/945604759fa9e6435c4e84a130df3853.webm?t=1727815132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/945604759fa9e6435c4e84a130df3853.mp4?t=1727815132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, fruits appear at the top of the screen and fall randomly. When two fruits of the same type touch, they merge to form a larger fruit. For example, two cherries combine to form a grape, two grapes combine to form a peach, and so on, until they form a watermelon. The challenge lies in managing the growing stack of fruits without letting them overflow the game area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/90a75d7538a4ff8e199438d9df4dee24.poster.avif?t=1727815132\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/90a75d7538a4ff8e199438d9df4dee24.webm?t=1727815132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/90a75d7538a4ff8e199438d9df4dee24.mp4?t=1727815132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suika Game has gained popularity for its simple and relaxing gameplay, becoming a hit among players looking for a light and fun pastime. Now available on Steam, the game is perfect for those seeking a casual and engaging experience.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out our next cozy game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/5af33c38713d9a56e1d93d0aa43ab355.avif?t=1727815132\" width=644 height=177 /></span>Watermelon Suika Game also known as the Watermelon Game, is a casual and addictive game where the goal is to stack and combine fruits of different sizes to create larger watermelons. The game mechanics resemble a \"match-3\" style, but with a fun twist where the fruits fall and roll across the screen with dynamic physics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/945604759fa9e6435c4e84a130df3853.poster.avif?t=1727815132\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/945604759fa9e6435c4e84a130df3853.webm?t=1727815132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/945604759fa9e6435c4e84a130df3853.mp4?t=1727815132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, fruits appear at the top of the screen and fall randomly. When two fruits of the same type touch, they merge to form a larger fruit. For example, two cherries combine to form a grape, two grapes combine to form a peach, and so on, until they form a watermelon. The challenge lies in managing the growing stack of fruits without letting them overflow the game area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/90a75d7538a4ff8e199438d9df4dee24.poster.avif?t=1727815132\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/90a75d7538a4ff8e199438d9df4dee24.webm?t=1727815132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2722740/extras/90a75d7538a4ff8e199438d9df4dee24.mp4?t=1727815132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suika Game has gained popularity for its simple and relaxing gameplay, becoming a hit among players looking for a light and fun pastime. Now available on Steam, the game is perfect for those seeking a casual and engaging experience.</p>",
